ActionChain
we use ActionChain class for this so firstly we need to import it
it helps to perform many action one after one
ActionChains is used to perform advanced user interactions

it works in 3 step
1. create object (once)
2. store action
3. then it perform (we have method .perform() for this)

Note: .perform() is essential to make the action get performed
.perform() is method that executes all the actions

actions.click(single_click).perform()   //click store one argument that is the name of element on which we are performing
actions.double_click(double_click).perform()    // for double click
actions.click(double_click).click(double_click).perform()       //this will also perform double click
action.context_click(right_click).perform()      //for right click  as we get context as we do right click so it is named as context_click()

